   "source": [
    "Suggested workflow\n",
    "\n",
    "Terminal 1: python tm_esn_optuna.py --n-trials 200 --fresh — starts the study.\n",
    "Terminal 2 (a few seconds later): python tm_esn_optuna.py --n-trials 200 — joins.\n",
    "\n",
    "This Notebook: Re-run first code cell occasionally to see the convergence curve.\n",
    "When the curve flatlines for 50–100 trials, both terminals are done or finishing.\n",
    "\n",
    "After both terminals exit, run tm_esn_optuna.run(report_only=True) (last code cell) once for the final report + validation + figure."
   ]
  },
